where I ended up today. So SAS was taught in certain classes that I had and in other classes,

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:58.440
the professors favored R. And I think the reason I really ended up on the R path was that my main

00:09:58.440 --> 00:10:06.200
thesis project was done in R. And so that really gave me a strong foundation so that when I started

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:14.359
