00:55:48.600 --> 00:55:55.239
that is engaged with a team. I didn't necessarily think I would be a remote employee. And that

00:55:55.239 --> 00:56:02.600
changed and most of us are now. And I think the single greatest advice is just pick up the phone,

00:56:02.600 --> 00:56:09.639
